          Hi Cybernetics class , so good to be here and to get to meet you all...my name is Matt Heffernan.
          and I'm coming to you from Larakia country in Darwin, Northern Territory. and I'd like to pay my respects
          to the elders past and present of this country, and the respective countries each of you are on today.
        </aside>
